divs: Sighting Detailsi was out smoking a cig and noticed something in the distance that looked weird. i went inside and asked my son to come and look and grabed my binoculars at witch time we noticed the object was a grocery bag flying in an updraft. I then gave the glasses to my son to look and he noticed objects in a differant area of the sky and thought they may be falling because of the way the were fluttering. At first there were four objects and suddanely one vanished. I then observed the objects through the glasses and noticed they seemed to remain in a triangular formation for the duration of the sighting. the objects eventually just vanished. To me and my son they looked like two litter bottles tumbling.
